- use Caveman only for low-risk terse work
- keep high-risk synthesis on normal prompts
- record use in status/checkpoint files

## If Always-On Mode Is Desired Later

- resolve the repo-root `.codex` file conflict intentionally first
- only then consider adding repo-local hook-based activation

